1
00:01:08,620 --> 00:01:11,370
Father, I have found the truth.

2
00:01:11,750 --> 00:01:14,010
I will clear the names of you and your men,

3
00:01:14,330 --> 00:01:16,410
and make the mastermind pay in blood.

4
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:33,789
A'deng.

5
00:01:34,250 --> 00:01:36,330
My father's dying words,

6
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,729
you heard them too, didn't you?

7
00:01:40,870 --> 00:01:42,000
I heard them.

8
00:01:43,789 --> 00:01:44,950
This demonic aura,

9
00:01:45,700 --> 00:01:47,580
the one on Vice Minister Zhou,

10
00:01:47,830 --> 00:01:48,910
the one on Ying,

11
00:01:49,330 --> 00:01:51,789
and the residual aura in the Kunlong Valley,

12
00:01:52,250 --> 00:01:53,660
all share the same origin.

13
00:01:53,660 --> 00:01:55,080
General Xie Lin's words

14
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:56,910
were definitely not dying nonsense.

15
00:01:56,910 --> 00:01:58,910
He was trapped and died in the valley.

16
00:01:58,910 --> 00:01:59,750
He must have discovered

17
00:01:59,750 --> 00:02:02,040
the truth about the collusion between the demons and traitors in the court,

18
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,330
so he was silenced.

19
00:02:04,290 --> 00:02:06,020
Even ten years after his death,

20
00:02:06,080 --> 00:02:07,880
his soul was still manipulated.

21
00:02:15,660 --> 00:02:16,870
I've investigated for ten years.

22
00:02:16,870 --> 00:02:19,290
I only found out someone secretly held back the reinforcements

23
00:02:19,290 --> 00:02:20,290
and cut off the provisions,

24
00:02:20,290 --> 00:02:22,500
but I couldn't find out who was behind it.

25
00:02:22,500 --> 00:02:23,410
Thinking about it now,

26
00:02:23,410 --> 00:02:24,950
to mobilize border provisions,

27
00:02:24,950 --> 00:02:26,079
intercept the secret letters for reinforcements,

28
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:27,750
and cover everything up after the war,

29
00:02:27,750 --> 00:02:29,950
framing my father for treason,

30
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:33,620
it's definitely not something an ordinary official could do.

31
00:02:34,079 --> 00:02:36,950
Who do you suspect?

32
00:02:44,910 --> 00:02:45,910
I don't know.

33
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:49,370
Ten years ago, if my uncle hadn't risked his reputation to protect me,

34
00:02:49,370 --> 00:02:51,250
and Chancellor Qin hadn't spoken up in the court,

35
00:02:51,250 --> 00:02:53,160
I would have died in the throne room long ago.

36
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:55,540
Over the years, they have treated me with immense kindness.

37
00:02:55,540 --> 00:02:56,800
But my father's words,

38
00:02:56,910 --> 00:02:58,200
the truth in the blood letter,

39
00:02:58,200 --> 00:03:00,120
and this pervasive demonic aura...

40
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,410
But I am sure

41
00:03:01,870 --> 00:03:04,330
you are also one of their targets.

42
00:03:05,660 --> 00:03:07,660
So I must protect you.

43
00:03:08,620 --> 00:03:11,040
No matter how big the conspiracy behind this is,

44
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:13,080
or how deep the waters in the court are,

45
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:15,340
I will investigate it to the end with you.

46
00:03:22,579 --> 00:03:23,200
General.

47
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:23,930
Miss A'deng.

48
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:28,000
An abbot from an ancient border temple is outside the camp asking to see you.

49
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,410
He says he has important matters

50
00:03:29,410 --> 00:03:31,470
and needs to speak with you in person.

51
00:03:32,700 --> 00:03:34,430
The abbot of an ancient temple?

52
00:03:34,829 --> 00:03:35,870
What does he want?

53
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:36,829
General,

54
00:03:37,660 --> 00:03:41,000
The abbot only said an ancient stele in the temple

55
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,790
has a deep connection with her.

56
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:45,079
He didn't say much else.

57
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,040
Got it.

58
00:03:47,700 --> 00:03:49,370
Please invite the abbot to the tent.

59
00:03:49,370 --> 00:03:50,700
We'll be there shortly.

60
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:51,950
Yes, sir.

61
00:04:09,830 --> 00:04:13,000
This Soul Lamp seems to be sensing something.

62
00:04:22,870 --> 00:04:23,910
Benefactors,

63
00:04:24,540 --> 00:04:26,400
I've been waiting for a long time.

64
00:04:26,410 --> 00:04:27,330
Please follow me.
